Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默地為妳著想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是悄悄藏在妳看不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以平時毫無察覺地生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一旦回過神來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為妳著想的那個人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會朦朧地浮現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果激烈地浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們就稱之為…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里 我今天做了烤奶油馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想讓爸爸媽媽吃到好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坑坑洼洼的 樣子糟糕得不好意思拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 一點也不會糟糕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裡面充滿了小愛的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為藍華今天去參加公司員工的旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有我跟愛麗絲兩個人一起練習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的聲音好好聽 好好聽哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為領航員最重要的是划船的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 難道妳心情不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓比妳年長的我來聽妳傾訴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事都不要客氣 告訴姐姐吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…我的左手太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近發覺我的左手非常笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟右手比 既無法拿好筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法寫出端正的字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那個…有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我正在懲罰左手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太依賴右手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都把所有事情交給右手做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把這當作理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有想辦法解決過這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近養了一隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:20.04,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 想要守護的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是領航員協會中最頂尖的橙色行星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是宿舍嚴禁養寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒關係嗎？愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手特訓？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠是小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為牠嘛嘛地叫 就取名為小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前牠被丟棄在路邊時 被我撿回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一個很寂寞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳才找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想找藍華前輩商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不巧她去公司員工的旅行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才找了燈里前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶回我們公司裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給亞利亞社長圓不隆咚的肚子造成大危機的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛 別叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不是奇怪的人…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是跟我同寢室的雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟妳說進房間前要敲門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才被妳嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾妳了 我是亞利亞公司的水無燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一位是我們公司的亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？愛麗絲 雅典娜前輩是不是長得跟剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一位唱著美妙歌聲的人有一點像？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就是她本人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三大精靈之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就屬雅典娜前輩的Canzone最為有名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}Canzone：義大利語「歌」的意思 這裡特指船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是傳說中的雅典娜前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩要住下來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前請先換上本公司的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那樣超級顯眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 小嘛會不會被雅典娜前輩發現呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止都還能應付過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雅典娜前輩超級喜歡發呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…好像豪華餐廳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一日三餐大都是在這裡解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 這杯水是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有番茄醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒發覺是雅典娜前輩幫她拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩又把全部的奶精放下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看雅典娜前輩那樣 她可是個很笨拙的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常在走廊上跌倒 還經常把飲料打翻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是連最重要的事情都會忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話的時候還會自己不小心把電話掛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說她有多笨拙的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概跟我的左手差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 不可以這樣說自己的前輩啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個都完全不在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚會跟亞利亞社長在您宿舍暫住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛找麻煩 這時候就要用左手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 請您先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛 吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎？小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小嘛的事告訴雅典娜前輩也沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 因為就算是前輩也改不了規定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳打算把牠就這麼藏著養嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳要這麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前 橙色行星的社長去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到小嘛就會想起牠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位社長跟小嘛很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一點也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀… 前輩洗得舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說應該已經暴露了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼呢？愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的猜拳遊戲…當然輸的都是左手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠在黑漆漆的地方會不會寂寞呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛在哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能…敗露了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩的歌唱得真是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 左手可能沒妳想的那麼笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩今天公司休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衣櫥裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去上學了 前輩請慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這能持續到什麼時候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}這就是移居的一大原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}好 正如上次課堂上所說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}大規模的AQUA移居計劃其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}已經是五十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}在那之前積累了無數次的失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨天那件事 可能已經有人發現小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手可能沒妳想的那麼笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手總是在背後默默地支持著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是今天起跟您同室的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲·卡羅爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛…小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:16:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛牠…小嘛牠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了呢？小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是被雅典娜前輩發現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後告訴公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…不能把事情往壞的地方想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到貓了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到愛麗絲的房間傳來貓的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打開了衣櫥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後牠就逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…不是雅典娜前輩丟掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩早就察覺到小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是為了掩飾小嘛的哭聲才特意唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…比左手還要沒用…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小嘛都保護不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你回來 小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘛也顯得很安心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小嘛而言 愛麗絲也是重要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到牠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道您剛才唱歌是為了找小嘛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也是為了掩飾小嘛的哭聲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都沒察覺到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛住進宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕 睡不著的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時妳也是這樣唱著歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是…還有 在我失眠的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也總是像這樣 是為我而唱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為歌聲…是要傳達給別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟公司商量過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳注意到了嗎？雖然太小不易察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這孩子確實擁有藍色的眼睛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子將成為橙色行星的新社長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色眼睛的守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手…是超級偉大的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在開始要練習向左手道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里 我把烤奶油馬鈴薯忘在廚房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什麼時候被爸爸吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下了一張字條…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫著「味道還可以 我期待妳下次的作品」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便吃人家的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟說「還可以」 這算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很過分對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也因此從低落中走了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心變得很溫暖 真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 可能我們大家不知何時起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在被別人默默支持著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人無法察覺地 默默地…悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐上晃前輩的鳳尾舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.72,0:24:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這麼高興也只有現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份 美好的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.71,0:24:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起度過美好的時光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:22.10,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:31.27,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:40.88,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:51.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:59.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:10.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:19.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:29.32,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:39.92,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:44.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:22.10,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}輕拂面頰的 溫柔的風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:31.27,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌聲中搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:40.88,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:51.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}閉上雙眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:59.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}是風的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:10.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}來 讓我們出發 向著閃亮的波濤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:19.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}臉上的笑容 從未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:29.32,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}快 傳達到彼方 把這份感動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:39.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}託付給清風 帶到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:44.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}水之精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:49.49,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水辺に映る いつもの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:57.06,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}穏やかに 流れる時間と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.75,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}移りゆく 季節の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:08.76,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}見つけたの 変わらぬ想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:13.07,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}聴いて 幸せの歌は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:19.69,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そう いつでも 心の中あふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:28.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.54,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:39.45,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:45.24,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:53.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:24:00.29,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:49.49,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不變的景色 倒映在水邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:57.06,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在緩緩流逝的時光和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.75,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不斷變化的季節中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:08.76,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}尋覓到 那不變的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:13.07,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}聽 那幸福的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:19.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}像這樣 一直 滿溢於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:28.26,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的夢想 都將實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.54,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我們 總會越過彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:39.45,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨後的彩虹 清澄的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:45.24,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鳥 總會展翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:53.66,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}收集起胸中的愛意 定會見到彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:24:00.29,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心中常懷愛意 定能越過彩虹


